<div class="jumbotron jumbotron-bottom jumbotron-bg-light" id="checklist">
    <div class="jumbotron-pd margin-top-33px">
        <div class="row display-block screen-margin-left-right">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <img src="~/Content/Images/medicare-quick.jpg" class="img-width" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8 margin-top-23px">
                <h3 class="bottom-pad-10px"><img src="~/Content/Images/info.png" class="info-img"/> <b>Medicare Checklist</b></h3>
                <h5>Follow these steps to get ready for Medicare before your 65th birthday:</h5>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mid-row"></div>
            <div class="row row-left bottom-pad-7px screen-margin-left-right">
                <div class="col-md-4 left-padding-0px">
                    <h5 class="heading-left">12-6 months before:</h5>
                    <ul class="medicare-ul-content">
                        <li class="li-item-left">Confirm you eligibility for Medicare at www.Medicare.gov. Not retiring yet? You can still get Medicare.</li>
                        <li class="li-item-left">Compare your options for getting more coverage than Original Medicare (Blue Cross NC Plans, retiree or employee benefits) </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 left-padding-0px">
                    <h5 class="heading-left">3 months before:</h5>
                    <ul class="medicare-ul-content">
                        <li class="li-item-left">Signup for Medicare Parts A &amp; B at ssa.gov/medicare. If you already have Social Security, you may be automatically enrolled.</li>
                        <li class="li-item-left">Enroll in Blue Medicare Advantage or Blue Medicare Supplement and Part D Prescription Drug Plan (If you don't have an employer/retiree Plan) </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 left-padding-0px">
                    <h5 class="heading-left">Birthday - 3 months before:</h5>
                    <ul class="medicare-ul-content">
                        <li class="li-item-left">Last chance to enroll for coverage under the Medicare Initial Enrollment Period!. If you wait until later, you will have to answer health questions on an application and could be turned down.</li>

                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
</div>

